QUAST 2.4 README

QUAST stands for QUality ASsessment Tool.
The tool evaluates genome assemblies by computing various metrics. 
You can find all project news and the latest version of the tool at 
http://sourceforge.net/projects/quast 

A comprehensive HTML user manual is available in manual.html file of the package 
or at http://quast.bioinf.spbau.ru/manual.html

Please refer to the INSTALL file for installation instructions.

If you use QUAST in your research, please include Gurevich et al., 2013 in your 
reference list:
Alexey Gurevich, Vladislav Saveliev, Nikolay Vyahhi and Glenn Tesler,
QUAST: quality assessment tool for genome assemblies,
Bioinformatics (2013) 29 (8): 1072-1075. doi: 10.1093/bioinformatics/btt086
First published online: February 19, 2013
